OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fwetter to end Tuesday as outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spread across the region. These
OL,8,Fcontinuing on-and-off overnight with
OL,9,Fdrier intervals. Cloud lowering and
OL,10,Fthickening, resulting in hill fog by
OL,11,Fdawn. Warm and muggy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FCloudy and misty with
OL,14,Fpatchy rain in the morning. Rain
OL,15,Feasing as the day progresses with
OL,16,Fbrighter spells developing as low
OL,17,Fcloud lifts. Feeling humid,
OL,18,Fparticularly if the sun emerges.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
