OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FGenerally drier to end the week with
OL,7,Fsunny spells by day after early cloud
OL,8,Fclears. The occasional spell of rain
OL,9,Fmay still occur. Remaining humid to
OL,10,Fbegin, fresher on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
